HEADWORD: Wardcorps
<hw>Ward"corps`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Wars</ets> +
<ets>corps</ets>.]</ety> <def>Guardian; one set to watch over
another.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Though thou preyedest Argus .
